<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Website</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }

        .page {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .project-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        table {
            width: auto; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 0; 
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            width: auto;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group input {
            width: calc(100% - 20px);
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 0; 
            margin-top: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My Website!</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div id="home" class="page">
        <h2>Home</h2>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Project:</th>
                <th>Description:</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Task 1.1:</td>
                <td>We learnt to create a HTML page, and add your own CSS styling. On top of this, we also got started using GITHUB.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Task 1.2:</td>
                <td>In this task, we explored responsive web design. We created a responsive web page that will work on any screen device size.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Task 1.3:</td>
                <td>In this task, we had to create our portfolio for this subject as a website instead of a list.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div id="projects" class="page">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="project-section">
            <h3>Task 1.1</h3>
            <p>In task 1.1, we ahd to create a HTML page, adn add your own CSS styling. This task was very informative, and allowed us to have a good base on what to do in the following tasks</p>
            
        </div>

        <div class="project-section">
            <h3>Task 1.2</h3>
            <p>In task 1.2, we explored responsive web design. We created a responsive web page that will work on any screen device size, and be able to be usable on any device. This task also asked us to explore javascript methods. </p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-section">
            <h3>Task 1.3</h3>
            <p>In task 1.3, we had to create our portfolio for this subject, as a website instead of using the portfolio feature in ontrack. This enabled us to put our learnings into practice and display what we learnt in a different way.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div id="contact" class="page">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone:</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
